igh quality of life numerous available sites and buildings ready for development to allow speed to market competitive reliable diverse largest public power company in the us competitive rates – lowest among peer utilities  transmission reliability since  diverse power generation portfolio of nuclear hydro fossil and renewables with over  nonemitting generation  tva will have a  reduction in carbon emissions by      in addition to competitively priced and reliable power companies considering the sevenstate tva region have access to a host of resources to aid in their location search including market research site evaluation and technical services as well as a number of financing and incentive programs  explore data on industrial product manufacturing from the tennessee valley and each of its subregion’s below  connect with us view all staff lee johnson  century boulevardsuite  ocp d nashville tn  partner login econdevtvacom p wwwtvasitescom  tennessee valley authority legal notices privacy policy foia no fear act data linking policy site created by atlas advertising  powered by community systems  site map about tvaabout tva economic developmentour teamalabamakentuckymiddle tennesseemississippinortheast valleysoutheast valleywest tennesseeeconomic development partnerslocal power companiesnews roomcontact usbusiness benefitstva region advantagesincentivesrates reliability  energy mixliving hereworkforcearea mapsservices  resourcescommunity developmentyoung talent  community livabilitysustainable communitiesrural developmentengineering  design serviceseconomic research  analysistarget industriesforeign direct investmentadvanced manufacturingaerospace and defensedata centersconsumer productsindustrial productstransportationrelated manufacturing